    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/e8e3ddbaa8a6e5665aa03dabd24a9933.poster.avif?t=1769736224\" width=640 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/e8e3ddbaa8a6e5665aa03dabd24a9933.webm?t=1769736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/e8e3ddbaa8a6e5665aa03dabd24a9933.mp4?t=1769736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Is a co-op, physics-based survival game set inside a regulated combat facility.</strong> <br>Enter increasingly difficult Boxes and build defenses that match your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/6cc9a3df80c737d6c332ec1fec4cf532.poster.avif?t=1769736224\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/6cc9a3df80c737d6c332ec1fec4cf532.webm?t=1769736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/6cc9a3df80c737d6c332ec1fec4cf532.mp4?t=1769736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build your own arsenal.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between runs, decide which items become part of your arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/053307a525e12d29098368e42d0d63fb.poster.avif?t=1769736224\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/053307a525e12d29098368e42d0d63fb.webm?t=1769736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/053307a525e12d29098368e42d0d63fb.mp4?t=1769736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive Boxes to unlock new and harder ones.</strong> <br>Higher difficulties unlock Unlimited Mode, where teams compete for top leaderboard positions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/81959ad21985b92201a965b95ca375f7.poster.avif?t=1769736224\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/81959ad21985b92201a965b95ca375f7.webm?t=1769736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269150/extras/81959ad21985b92201a965b95ca375f7.mp4?t=1769736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every run is randomized.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize all tools given to maximise your chance of survival. Adapt together, make fast decisions and use everything available to survive. <br>  </p>",
